<section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>
            <%= h1 %>
        </h1>
        <p>Watch <%= subject %> live stream free today. The best high-quality links for <%= subject %> fans on
                    FootyBite.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="container">
    <div class="hub-content-wrapper">
        <div class="hub-main-content">
            <article class="seo-article">
                <h2>How to Watch <%= subject %> Live Stream?</h2>
                <p>If you are looking for a reliable <strong>
                        <%= subject %> live stream
                    </strong>, you have come to the right place. FootyBite (often searched as Footybyte or Fotybyte) is
                    the world's leading platform for sports fans who want to watch their favorite games without paying
                    for expensive cable subscriptions.</p>

                <p>Whether it's a high-stakes match or a regular season game, we provide multiple high-definition links
                    to ensure you never miss a second of the action. Our platform is optimized for all devices, meaning
                    you can watch <%= subject %> on your phone, tablet, or desktop with ease.</p>

                <h3>Why Choose FootyBite for <%= subject %>?</h3>
                <p>There are many streaming sites out there, but FootyBite stands out for several reasons. First and
                    foremost is our commitment to quality. We aggregate links from the most trusted sources on the
                    internet to bring you the best possible viewing experience.</p>

                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Free Access:</strong> No hidden fees, no subscriptions, no credit cards. Just free
                        sports.</li>
                    <li><strong>HD Quality:</strong> We prioritize 1080p and 720p streams for crystal-clear visuals.
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Mobile Optimized:</strong> Our site is fast and responsive on all mobile browsers.</li>
                    <li><strong>Real-Time Updates:</strong> Links are updated every hour to ensure they are always
                        working.</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Frequently Asked Questions about <%= subject %>
                </h3>
                <div class="hub-faq">
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h4>Is <%= subject %> really free on FootyBite?</h4>
                        <p>Yes! FootyBite is a free link aggregation service. We do not charge users for access to any
                            of the sports streams we list.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h4>Do I need to create an account?</h4>
                        <p>No registration is required. We value your privacy and want to make the process as fast as
                            possible.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h4>What if a stream stops working?</h4>
                        <p>We provide multiple mirror links for every match. If one link goes down, simply try another
                            one from the list.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <% if (events && events.length> 0) { %>
                <div class="match-section">
                    <h2 class="section-title">Upcoming <%= subject %> Matches</h2>
                    <div class="match-grid">
                        <% events.forEach(event=> { %>
                            <%- include('match_card_partial', { event: event }) %>
                                <% }) %>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <% } else { %>
                    <div class="empty-state">
                        <h3>No live matches for <%= subject %> at the moment</h3>
                        <p>Check back soon for the latest schedules and links.</p>
                    </div>
                    <% } %>
        </div>

        <aside class="hub-sidebar">
            <div class="sidebar-card">
                <h3>ðŸ”¥ Popular Matches</h3>
                <div class="mini-match-list">
                    <% events.slice(0, 10).forEach(event=> { %>
                        <a href="/<%= event.url %>" class="mini-match-item">
                            <span class="mini-sport">
                                <%= event.sport.toUpperCase() %>
                            </span>
                            <span class="mini-name">
                                <%= event.name %>
                            </span>
                        </a>
                        <% }) %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </aside>
    </div>
</section>